<pb n="0237a" xml:id="I01.0089.0237a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0237a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 89</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0237a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>舜禪師等百餘人造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0237a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0237a0101">□邑主禪師舜　象主劉□□
<lb ed="I" n="0237a02" type="honorific"/>□夫<note n="0237001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">朙＝明【史】</note><note n="0237001" resp="ihp" type="mod">朙【佛拓】，明【史】</note><app n="0237001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朙</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0237001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【原】">朙</rdg></app>萬象。仰之誰得其□。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a03" type="honorific"/>攸攸<note n="0237002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡉵＝兆【史】</note><note n="0237002" resp="ihp" type="mod">𡉵【佛拓】，兆【史】</note><app n="0237002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">兆</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡉵</rdg></app>庶。俯之熟測其際。唯大
<lb ed="I" n="0237a04" type="honorific"/>□靈尊。威神无量。籠括空有。獨
<lb ed="I" n="0237a05" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">在</unclear>環中。演三乘於苦海。為眾生
<lb ed="I" n="0237a06" type="honorific"/>之樑棟。隨六道之去來。示北首
<lb ed="I" n="0237a07" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">於</unclear>雙林。其有舜禪師者。閑居味
<lb ed="I" n="0237a08" type="honorific"/>□。捨苦<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">樂</unclear>於一心。<note n="0237003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">豦＝據【史】</note><note n="0237003" resp="ihp" type="mod">豦【佛拓】，據【史】</note><app n="0237003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">據</lem><rdg wit="【原】">豦</rdg></app>披无<note n="0237004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31090"/>＝罦【史】</note><note n="0237004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31090"/>【佛拓】，罦【史】</note><app n="0237004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">罦</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31090"/></rdg></app>。恒
<lb ed="I" n="0237a09" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">方</unclear>便以開導。欲使未曾有法。給
<lb ed="I" n="0237a10" type="honorific"/>□荼心。无緣之慈。引其鄙意。復
<lb ed="I" n="0237a11" type="honorific"/>有<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">劉</unclear>洪安。劉專。劉嶠常。劉獻伯。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a12" type="honorific"/>□□□。劉黑等。性與天道。直置
<lb ed="I" n="0237a13" type="honorific"/>□□□慍不改其容。榮辱何關
<lb ed="I" n="0237a14" type="honorific"/>在□。□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">鷲</unclear>鸑之長歎。慨羅預之
<lb ed="I" n="0237a15" type="honorific"/>見<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">損</unclear>。傷慧日□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">傳</unclear>。痛金棺於
<lb ed="I" n="0237a16" type="honorific"/>長夜。遂率宗門一百餘人。共興
<lb ed="I" n="0237a17" type="honorific"/>□攝之心。俱起□天之念。欲令
<lb ed="I" n="0237a18" type="honorific"/>甘露久光。金河□盡。法幢更暉。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a19" type="honorific"/>慧炬復照。即敬造<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">西</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">方</unclear><note n="0237005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31091"/>＝阿【史】</note><note n="0237005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31091"/>【佛拓】，阿【史】</note><app n="0237005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">阿</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31091"/></rdg></app><note n="0237006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB02793"/>＝彌【史】</note><note n="0237006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02793"/>【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0237006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB02793"/></rdg></app>陀
<lb ed="I" n="0237a20" type="honorific"/>像。并觀音。大勢。白毫宛轉。與五
<lb ed="I" n="0237a21" type="honorific"/>山如爭隆。青目分明。共四海如
<lb ed="I" n="0237a22" type="honorific"/><note n="0237007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥪰＝競【史】</note><note n="0237007" resp="ihp" type="mod">𥪰【佛拓】，競【史】</note><app n="0237007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥪰</rdg></app>朗。一一相好。不得兼二以觀
<lb ed="I" n="0237a23" type="honorific"/>之。頌德弗閑。豈復更□於餘偈。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a24" type="honorific"/>將知巍巍難量。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">猶</unclear>山玉之對川
<lb ed="I" n="0237a25" type="honorific"/>長。唐唐易睹。若<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">二</unclear>日之現華池。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a26" type="honorific"/>昔不傾不動。由□木如往生。不
<lb ed="I" n="0237a27" type="honorific"/>穢不濁。因聚沙之微業。況功同
<lb ed="I" n="0237a28" type="honorific"/>□石。神等育王。豈使催時之獸
<lb ed="I" n="0237a29" type="honorific"/>虛馳如往返。減<note n="0237008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">笇＝算【史】</note><note n="0237008" resp="ihp" type="mod">笇【佛拓】，算【史】</note><app n="0237008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">算</lem><rdg wit="【原】">笇</rdg></app>之禽空驟於
<lb ed="I" n="0237a30" type="honorific"/>去來。乃為頌曰。　　二儀覆載。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a31" type="honorific"/>万品有緣。受業各異。感果相牽。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a32" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">御</unclear>龍奕世。英倫比肩。<note n="0237009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠜇＝刻【史】</note><note n="0237009" resp="ihp" type="mod">𠜇【佛拓】，刻【史】</note><app n="0237009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">刻</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠜇</rdg></app>作能仁。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a33" type="honorific"/>相好殊妍。昞若畫石。猶月昇天
<lb ed="I" n="0237a34" type="honorific"/>□□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">飾</unclear>。沾及无邊。四恩九居。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a35" type="honorific"/>□茲福田。慈氏三會。上首俱前。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a36" type="honorific"/>□之金石。□□斯年。
<lb ed="I" n="0237a37" type="honorific"/>　大齊武<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">平</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">元</unclear>年歲在攝提星
<lb ed="I" n="0237a38" type="honorific"/>　□□月□寶鐘經始故記之
<lb ed="I" n="0237a39" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　大施主劉□□</p>
